---
title: Char Siu Pork Belly & Sticky Eggplant with Ginger Rice & Peanuts
description: What’s an instant way to bring bold, international flavours to pork? Add this sweet 'n' salty char siu paste to melt-in-your-mouth pork
belly. Teamed with sticky braised eggplant, plus an aromatic ginger rice, this meal will make your tastebuds sing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/char-siu-pork-belly-sticky-eggplant-47965dd6.jpg
